# Delivery pool
A full stack web application that allow users to search for people ordering food near them to save delivery cost.

### Technologies
MERN stack
Mongoose, Express, React, Node.js 

### Approach taken
Used JWT and react-cookies to verify, send and receive user information in a stateless application
Used both google Geocoding API and mongoDB $geonear aggregation pipeline in order to obtain the coordinates of a user location and return a list of other users nearby


Link
 https://delivery-pool.herokuapp.com/
